KORISNO RAZNO
-------------
from scratch (odlican veoma prost note taking app, single page autosave ...)
jpegoptim (odlican prost automatski optimizator jpg slika - ima ga u officijelnim repo)

CLEANUP:
--------
1. sudo apt-get clean
2. sudo apt-get autoremove
3. sudo apt-get install localepurge
4. sudo apt-get install deborphan
    4.1 sudo deborphan | xargs sudo apt-get -y remove --purge

DEVELOPMENT
